    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily commuter. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches on the side panels and some minor paint oxidation on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some light staining consistent with its age. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for affordable transportation without the need for cosmetic perfection.",
