    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained specimen that exemplifies mechanical excellence and sophisticated styling. This vehicle has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a commanding presence, while the interior offers a refined environment for the discerning driver. It represents a premier opportunity for those seeking a balance of proven durability and contemporary luxury.",
