    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been a total joy to drive. It\u2019s super reliable and perfect for anyone looking for a great ride that\u2019s been well-cared for. I\u2019ve loved having it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
