    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and serves as a reliable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though you may find a couple of minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, with all features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound; I have documented every scheduled oil change and tire rotation, ensuring a smooth, responsive ride. It is a solid, honest car that offers a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
