    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to hit the road with you. I've taken great care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as appreciated. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
