    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example features a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Crucial preventative maintenance has been completed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains composed with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offering distinct valve mapping for varied rebound characteristics, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and leak-free. While the finish shows minor stone peppering consistent with spirited use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and mechanical harmony.",
